      <gmd:abstract>
        <gco:CharacterString>A virtual lab to compile comprehensive marine biodiversity time series in Europe and disentangle the major patterns and drivers of long-term biodiversity trends using various taxonomic and functional diversity metrics, species traits, and environmental variables. The vLab has been created by using the LifeWatch NaaVRE platform.</gco:CharacterString>
      </gmd:abstract>

